"v.专门研究 【英】 v. 专门研究(limit to a particular activity or subject) 【记】 special（特殊的；sp eci[种类]+al→[属于 ]种类的→特别的）+ize v. 专门研究 【记】源于: special(n专车; 专刊; adj 特别的; 特殊的; 专门的) 【反】dabble(v 涉足; 浅显的了解)dabbler(n 业余爱好者)－specialist(n 专家) 【记】special + ize specialize (v.)  1610s, ""to indicate specially,"" from special (adj.) + -ize, perhaps on model of French spécialiser. Sense of ""engage in a special study or line of business"" is first attested 1881; biological sense is from 1851. Related: Specialized; specializing."
